{
  "stem": "2906.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you were looking for somebody, if you have relatives, if you have sometime friends, If you--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were maybe 5,000-- 5,000 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there we were waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're all Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't a Christian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my doctor was a-- was-- was Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he saved my life and my--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Hallein.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My daughter was born in Hallein.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] when I got-- from everything, I got high blood pressure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before, the Jewish doctors want to take away the baby from you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said you can't have it, because if you'll have a baby you'll die.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, if I lost my whole family, and I can't have a child, I don't want to live either.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this Ukraine doctor came, and I went to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, don't worry, I'll see that you'll have a-- a-- a-- a child.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And don't listen to anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when my daughter was born, he-- he-- he helped me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was just wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think a long time-- we-- '45 to 1946.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were five years in-- in Hallein.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we got papers to--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a lot of people--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from Poland, from-- as a matter of fact, before I worked with children from the Holocaust, I went in a seminar.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before my daughter was born, I went to Linz, in a seminar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I came back, I worked with children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Usually, the children were from Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People came from Russia, their children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the people who came from the-- from the camp from Germany didn't have children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were telling all the-- the terrible things-- the way they burned the people, the way they-- it was-- you couldn't-- it's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
